    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将在关键通胀数据公布前维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-18/ecb-set-to-hold-rates-before-key-inflation-data-arrive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将于周四维持利率不变，等待通胀出现进一步改善的证据，然后再继续 6 月份的降息。彭博社记者 Lizzy Burden 在法兰克福报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-18/ecb-set-to-hold-rates-before-key-inflation-data-arrive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:47:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
